<H3>Simple API for XML (SAX)</H3>

<P>An interface shared by a variety of XML Parsers. If for some reason, 
AElfred becomes a thing of the past, Chimera can switch to using any
SAX-Compliant XML parser to do its parsing. SAX can be downloaded from
<A HREF="http://www.megginson.com/SAX/sax.html">Megginson Technologies's website</A>
.</P>
